{
  "stem": "18102.3",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And if we didn't catch this last train out of Bialystok to Vilna, we wouldn't, at least in a conventional way, be able to go to Vilna.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we packed, said our goodbyes.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody came with us to the [NON-ENGLISH], the, the, the train station, and we left for Vilna.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Again, a memory that I will never forget, that scene at the train station with what seemed like thousands of people rushing about, trying to get on trains.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, whether they all knew what my father knew or not, there were people running from and running to, and it was total mayhem and confusion and, and chaos.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We got on board a train.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I, because of my age, was given a window seat.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This was a most coveted occasion-- vantage point, to be able to sit at the window because people were sitting on boxes and baggage and, and, and standing.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Usually the, the the train ride to Vilna, in conventional time, was a couple hours, at most.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This took all night, because the train would stop in the middle of the night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We would hear shouts.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Sometimes we would hear gunfire.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "People with voices could be heard in the distance sometimes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So it was very eerie and scary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I would always awake during those intervals, because once the train started to roll again, I would nod off to sleep, of course, but would be awakened the very next time it stopped.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it stopped more than it went, because it took so long to get to Vilna.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We arrived in the morning, actually.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It took all night.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I spotted my father-- because I remember he was in a [NON-ENGLISH], a hat.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And our eyes met for, for a fraction of a second.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
